01:21:24.280 --> 01:21:26.482
Come on, let's go.

01:21:29.052 --> 01:21:30.987
She killed Travis.

01:21:31.020 --> 01:21:32.655
She killed Travis.
- Run! Run! Run!

01:21:32.688 --> 01:21:34.657
